{"tid":994104,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"狠劈80萬！康田苑售520萬　創同類新低","createTime":"2019-01-24T12:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T10:06:14.000Z","uid":174649,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1b32db3a0d3b22a9b6d2b2cdac55c3f52cac05fa","tid":994104,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190124/photo/bkn-20190124171127520-0124_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190124173811\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190124%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190124171127520-0124_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190124173811&h=c35914f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n未補價自由市場居屋屢現跌價成交。世紀21聯誠謝寶昭稱，藍田老牌居屋康田苑B座中層7室，實用面積420方呎，上月開價600萬元放售，減至520萬元才獲承接，呎價約12,381元，創同類單位2017年後新低價。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該屋苑為早期居屋，一手業主無須補地價已可在自由市場轉售。"},{"pid":"354c292f9873540c5d1e6650b22adff4aeebefa5","tid":994104,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"市區居屋都劈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed8948d5c93d988c9766c241d8ce77ad5336106","tid":994104,"uid":195334,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"未補㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 補咗都貴囉"},{"pid":"24e90860efff5eb128c9cf74b477b5b79ae98b65","tid":994104,"uid":57848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bed8948d5c93d988c9766c241d8ce77ad5336106","tid":994104,"uid":195334,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"未補㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 補咗都貴囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"唔洗補地價同私樓有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c8262c0070af84aed6da96f88270a80377b612","tid":994104,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"